# Useful Ocaml commands
To create a new version:
```
  opam switch create 4.07.0
```

Switch compiler version
```
  opam switch 4.07.0
```

# basics
put the folder for your image and inside have a Dockerfile for it
to build a docker image run:
```
  docker build -t TAG_NAME .
```

to see your images:
```
  docker images
```

to create/run a container based on that image run:
```
  docker run -it TAG_NAME
```

#
to create/run a container with a volum to my cs421 code:
```
  docker run -it -v ~/cs421:/home/opam/opam-repository/cs421 cs421
```



